The notification required under subsection (a) of this section shall:
Be mailed by the Administration to the most recent address provided by the cosigner in accordance with § 16-107(b) of this article; and
Contain the following information:
The name, address, and date of birth of the minor charged with the violation;
Identification of the moving violation charged;
If the citation was issued for a speeding violation, the speed at which the minor is alleged to have driven and the maximum lawful speed at the location of the alleged violation;
The amount of the fine specified in the citation; and
The number of points that may be assessed against the minor.
